        site. Docusaurus did a ton of this work for me. Since it's built for
        documentation, it has a ton of features to sort and organize the content
        you're looking to present. Eventually, I settled on 5 distinct
        categories to organize the terms I was presenting.
      </p>
      <br />
      <br />
